<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
    <div class="row align-items-start">
        <div class="col">
            <h1 class="display-4">Fountain Brothers</h1>
            <p class="lead mt-3">
                The Fountain Brothers Club was founded in 2007 in Egbeda, Lagos
                State, Nigeria. Our journey began with informal evening
                gatherings where we discovered our common bond - our Ekiti
                heritage and shared values.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Image Gallery -->
<div class="container-fluid p-0 my-5">
    <div class="row g-0">
        {{#each galleryImages}}
        <div class="col-md-4 gallery-item">
            <img src="{{this}}" class="img-fluid w-100" alt="Gallery image">
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Mission Section -->
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row align-items-start">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At Fountain Brothers of Nigeria, we empower individuals and
                communities to drive sustainable transformation and positive
                change.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Vision Section -->
<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row align-items-end">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                Our vision is to liberate our community from poverty, unlocking
                a brighter future through education, self-awareness, and
                economic empowerment.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>